{"data":[{"date":"09:29 05/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Liverpool l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ecdc t\u1ee9c Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Liverpool g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c c\u1ea3 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/klopp-noi-gi-ve-qua-bom-tan-bat-ngo-fabinho-172-187241.html\" target=\"_blank\">qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd Fabinho 45-50 tri\u1ec7u Euro</span> m\u1edf m\u00e0n k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, khi m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n li\u00ean h\u1ec7 g\u00ec gi\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Champions League v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Monaco.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Fabinho c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Fabinho c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n binh Fabinho c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i h\u01a1n khi Fabinho t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Man Utd qua c\u00e1c phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, v\u1eady n\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1eddi chung kia n\u1eabng tay tr\u00ean trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00ednh ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cKh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man Utd li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3.\u201d \u2013 Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o ch\u1ecdc t\u1ee9c Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u1ee7a Fabinho.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 nghe l\u1eddi ra l\u1eddi v\u00e0o v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, n\u00f3 ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t thi\u1ec7t m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Monaco \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Man Utd nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u00e0nh cho t\u00f4i th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Liverpool m\u1edbi nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ef1 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Fabinho l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 1/7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eadn m\u1ed9t n\u0103m, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Naby Keita t\u1eeb RB Leipzig v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-sang-liverpool-them-mot-lan-cai-tat-vao-mu-172-187307.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/fabinho-sang-liverpool-them-mot-lan-cai-tat-vao-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-sang-liverpool-them-mot-lan-cai-tat-vao-mu-172-187307.html\">Fabinho sang Liverpool: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n c\u00e1i t\u00e1t v\u00e0o MU</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i, c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng Fabinho sang Liverpool qu\u00e1 nhanh, qu\u00e1 nguy hi\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0 phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"920","checkdouble":"190403"},{"date":"09:15 05/07","title":"Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/willian-ca-ngoi-neymar-giua-nhung-chi-trich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Willian ca ng\u1ee3i Neymar gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea tin ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n n\u1eefa t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Willian \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Neymar</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kho\u1ea3ng n\u1eeda th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 khai m\u1ea1c, Neymar v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3. 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u1edbi Mexico, ch\u00ednh Neymar l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc cho Brazil \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1eadt ra, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Roberto Firmino \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho Selecao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian ca ng\u1ee3i Neymar gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Willian ca ng\u1ee3i Neymar gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/willian-ca-ngoi-neymar-giua-nhung-chi-trich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Willian ca ng\u1ee3i Neymar gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien-421-190281.html\" target=\"_blank\">Neymar v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0103n v\u1ea1 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0</span> \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Willian, anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Neymar trong \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ebf n\u00e0o\u201d, Willian ca ng\u1ee3i Neymar. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111i t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 may m\u1eafn.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNeymar l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u00e1ch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois phat bieu ve DT Anh\" title=\"Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-bong-da-la-da-bong-da-bong-la-bong-da.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Willian d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Courtois</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nC\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup l\u00e0 B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u00e0o 1h ng\u00e0y 7/7 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9 gi\u1eefa Willian v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Chelsea, Thibaut Courtois. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Courtois khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d, Willian n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Courtois: Alisson, Ederson, Cassio. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/douglas-costa-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-421-190341.html\">Brazil nh\u1eadn tin vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kompany-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-bi-vs-brazil-421-190392.html\">Kompany: B\u1ec9 s\u1ee3 g\u00ec c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Brazil?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-thang-tien-tu-ket-chat-thep-quyen-lan-trong-nhung-vu-dieu-samba-421-190290.html\">Brazil th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft: Ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p quy\u1ec7n l\u1eabn trong nh\u1eefng v\u0169 \u0111i\u1ec7u Samba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vuot-qua-nhat-dt-bi-da-san-sang-truoc-brazil-421-190268.html\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-den-di-tiem-phong-cung-se-an-va-voi-bac-si-421-190267.html\">Neymar \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i ti\u00eam ph\u00f2ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0103n v\u1ea1 v\u1edbi b\u00e1c s\u0129!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"919","checkdouble":"190404"},{"date":"09:59 05/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n binh Fabinho c\u1ee7a Liverpool kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</h2><h2>Fabinho kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-noi-fabinho-dang-gia-nhat-cua-chuyen-nhuong-mu-172-162081.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fabinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man United \u01b0u ti\u00ean</span> chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 sau khi gi\u00fap Monaco gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ligue 1 v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c. V\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Fabinho \u00edt l\u00e2u sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabinho kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi MU nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fabinho kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi MU nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/13/Fabinho-khong-lien-he-voi-MU-nhu-bao-chi-don-thoi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 trong b\u00e0i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u00ean t\u1edd FourFourTwo g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Fabinho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c anh ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Man United nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man United. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i bu\u1ed5i th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i Monaco. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Man United\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Fabinho kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n suy ngh\u0129 khi Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u khi Liverpool b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng bu\u1ed3n khi ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Monaco. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB mang l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNgay khi Liverpool b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. Khi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00e0o h\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 b\u1ea1n th\u00ec b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i h\u00e0nh l\u00fd v\u00e0 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vinh d\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-0507-mu-va-chelsea-no-bom-tan-cung-luc-184-190395.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 05/07: MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d c\u00f9ng l\u00fac</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-ban-willian-cho-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien-172-190352.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian cho MU v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"918","checkdouble":"190405"},{"date":"10:08 05/07","title":"Ronaldo b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/dan-anh-bao-ve-thoi-an-va-cua-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e0n em, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2>Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang?<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Mexico v\u1eeba qua, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u01b0a Selecao th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ef1c x\u1ea5u khi \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, b\u1edfi anh s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u1eadt gi\u1ea3i Oscar n\u1ebfu chuy\u1ec3n sang nghi\u1ec7p di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, HLV \u0110T Ireland cho r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/neymar-den-di-tiem-phong-cung-se-an-va-voi-bac-si-421-190267.html\" target=\"_blank\">Neymar \u0111i kh\u00e1m c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0103n v\u1ea1 v\u1edbi\u2026 b\u00e1c s\u0129</span>.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u00e0y, \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i h\u00e0nh tinh\u201d Ronaldo de Lima l\u1ea1i ngh\u0129 kh\u00e1c. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3i n\u00f3. \u00dd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Neymar, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u00e0o h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Ronaldo-bao-ve-thoi-an-va-cua-Neymar-truoc-nhung-chi-trich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Ronaldo b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNeymar l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng minh \u1edf nh\u1eefng pha di chuy\u1ec3n, v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng pha va ch\u1ea1m. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cKhi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. Ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eb3ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i b\u1eadn t\u00e2m. Nh\u1eefng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n l\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Jose Mourinho c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. J<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/sau-neymar-gio-lai-co-dien-vien-henderson-421-190346.html\" target=\"_blank\">ordan Henderson c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n</span>, v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 to l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Harry Maguire c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m \u201cth\u1ee3 l\u1eb7n.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ronaldo b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf. Neymar m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i. \u1ede k\u1ef3 World Cup 2014 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, anh c\u0169ng b\u1ecb h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Colombia ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o, v\u00e0 su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Clip C\u0110V Mexico di\u1ec5n l\u1ea1i th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/3/mexico.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien-421-190281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien-421-190281.html\">Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean t\u1eeb b\u1ecf nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ngh\u1ec1 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Mexico 2-0, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-che-duoc-ronaldo-va-messi-ru-ve-nuoc-neymar-mim-cuoi-noi-khong-421-190277.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/anh-che-duoc-ronaldo-va-messi-ru-ve-nuoc-neymar-mim-cuoi-noi-khong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-che-duoc-ronaldo-va-messi-ru-ve-nuoc-neymar-mim-cuoi-noi-khong-421-190277.html\">\u1ea2nh ch\u1ebf: \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi r\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, Neymar m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, nh\u01b0ng Brazil v\u1eabn \u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga chinh chi\u1ebfn. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Neymar t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Ronaldo v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"917","checkdouble":"190406"},{"date":"09:40 05/07","title":"Matuidi tin Mbappe s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn h\u1ea1 Uruguay \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/matuidi-khang-dinh-mbappe-se-toa-sang-hon-nua.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Blaise Matuidi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sao tr\u1ebb Kylian Mbappe s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng d\u00f9 Uruguay c\u00f3 b\u00e0y binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Mbappe r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/8 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Argentina. Mbappe ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 cho Les Bleus 1 qu\u1ea3 penalty trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap \u0111\u00f3, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 2 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i d\u01b0\u1edbi 20 l\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i World Cup sau \u201cVua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d Pele.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 kinh ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f4 v\u00e0n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Jorge Sampaoli. V\u00e0 Uruguay ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Uruguay kh\u00f3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Mbappe\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng d\u00f9 Uruguay b\u00e0y binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn ra sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mbappe s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng d\u00f9 Uruguay b\u00e0y binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn ra sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/matuidi-khang-dinh-mbappe-se-toa-sang-hon-nua.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Matuidi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Mbappe s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng d\u00f9 Uruguay b\u00e0y binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn ra sao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 Matuidi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng Mbappe ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Uruguay s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f3a ch\u1eb7t anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTheo d\u00f5i Mbappe ng\u00e0y qua ng\u00e0y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu nh\u00f3c n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec9nh d\u00f9 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u00edt \u1ecfi \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cK\u00e8m c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhanh. V\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb \u1edf kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cK\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Uruguay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng n\u00e0o th\u00ec Mbappe c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Mbappe:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/varane-mbappe-mang-hinh-bong-cua-ro-beo-469-190173.html\">Varane: Mbappe mang h\u00ecnh b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ro b\u00e9o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-tang-boc-mbappe-len-may-sau-tran-dai-thang-argentina-469-190086.html\">Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng Mbappe</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"916","checkdouble":"190408"},{"date":"10:13 05/07","title":"Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n binh Fabinho c\u1ee7a Liverpool kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</h2><h2>Fabinho kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-noi-fabinho-dang-gia-nhat-cua-chuyen-nhuong-mu-172-162081.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fabinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man United \u01b0u ti\u00ean</span> chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 sau khi gi\u00fap Monaco gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ligue 1 v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c. V\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Fabinho \u00edt l\u00e2u sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabinho kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi MU nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fabinho kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi MU nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/13/Fabinho-khong-lien-he-voi-MU-nhu-bao-chi-don-thoi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 trong b\u00e0i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u00ean t\u1edd FourFourTwo g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Fabinho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c anh ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Man United nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man United. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i bu\u1ed5i th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i Monaco. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Man United\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Fabinho kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n suy ngh\u0129 khi Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u khi Liverpool b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng bu\u1ed3n khi ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Monaco. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB mang l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNgay khi Liverpool b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. Khi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00e0o h\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 b\u1ea1n th\u00ec b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i h\u00e0nh l\u00fd v\u00e0 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vinh d\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-0507-mu-va-chelsea-no-bom-tan-cung-luc-184-190395.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 05/07: MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d c\u00f9ng l\u00fac</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-ban-willian-cho-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien-172-190352.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian cho MU v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"915","checkdouble":"190409"},{"date":"10:39 05/07","title":"Trung v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p th\u1edf ph\u00e0o khi \"s\u00e1t th\u1ee7\" Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Adil Rami \u0111\u00e3 th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m khi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cavani d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p.</h2><h2>Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rami th\u1edf ph\u00e0o khi s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rami th\u1edf ph\u00e0o khi s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/rami-tho-phao-khi-sat-thu-cavani-chan-thuong-nang.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ghi 2 b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 c\u1ee7a Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ldbd-uruguay-xac-nhan-kha-nang-ra-san-cua-cavani-o-tran-gap-dt-phap-421-190362.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cavani \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp t\u1ec5nh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span>. Ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u0129 c\u0169ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n khoeo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCavani \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i \u1edf bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 T\u01b0. V\u00e0 anh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i Nizhny Novgorod.</div>\r\n<h2>Rami th\u1edf ph\u00e0o nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Adil Rami kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Didier Deschamps kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Cavani. B\u1edfi v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTh\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc khi Cavani kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t c\u1ee7a Uruguay mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cEdinson Cavani v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, anh \u1ea5y c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao n\u1eefa. V\u1eady n\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c anh \u1ea5y ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i t\u1eebng b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian. T\u00f4i t\u1eebng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i khoa h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. Do \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu Cavani mu\u1ed1n ra s\u00e2n, anh \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t khoa h\u1ecdc. T\u00f4i th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1p v\u00e0 Uruguay s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Brazil ho\u1eb7c B\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 4 \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs Uruguay:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-uruguay-xac-nhan-kha-nang-ra-san-cua-cavani-o-tran-gap-dt-phap-421-190362.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 Uruguay c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/suarez-uruguay-se-ha-phap-ma-khong-can-cavani-421-190310.html\">Suarez: Uruguay s\u1ebd h\u1ea1 Ph\u00e1p m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n Cavani</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"914","checkdouble":"190410"},{"date":"10:50 05/07","title":"Chelsea vu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t con m\u1ed3i v\u00ec... Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Argentina \u2013 Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n</h2><h2>Chelsea n\u1ebfm tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eafng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea. H\u1ecd qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Alvaro Morata &ndash; bom t\u1ea5n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, trong khi Michy Batshuayi c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1 h\u01a1n l\u00e0 bao. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a The Blues l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Olivier Giroud, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u0103m nay 32 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady, h\u1ecd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecfi mua Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd Alvaro Morata, v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Chelsea v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u01b0ng \u00fd v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Argentina \u0111\u00e3 quay ngo\u1eaft 180 \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juve, sau khi anh nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y CLB chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111em v\u1ec7 Cristiano Ronaldo. T\u00e1i h\u1ee3p si\u00eau sao B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e1ng m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc, v\u00e0 Higuain kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1i t\u1eeb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Higuain t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea v\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Higuain l\u1ea5y Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Higuain t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea v\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo anh trai v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n &ndash; Nicolas Higuain cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Hi\u1ec7n nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 CLB n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c. Gonzalo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Gonzalo h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, CLB, HLV, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n nh\u1ea3m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft Gonzalo c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi HLV Sarri (ng\u01b0\u1eddi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea). Nh\u01b0ng theo t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft, Sarri v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Gonzalo \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Turin v\u00e0 CLB c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 Gonzalo ra \u0111i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Higuain t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat kh\u00e1c, ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Higuain, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 m\u00e1t sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, v\u00e0 \u0111ang ch\u1edd t\u1eebng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span><br>\r\nC\u00fa s\u1ed1c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro,...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/truyen-thong-chau-au-deu-khang-dinh-95-ronaldo-sang-juventus-180-190379.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/truyen-thong-chau-au-deu-khang-dinh-95-ronaldo-sang-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/truyen-thong-chau-au-deu-khang-dinh-95-ronaldo-sang-juventus-180-190379.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh 95% Ronaldo c\u00f3 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Italia \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo cho Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro ngay...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"913","checkdouble":"190411"},{"date":"10:59 05/07","title":"Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u1ed5 2 \"bom t\u1ea5n\" Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/real-duoc-khuyen-no-2-bom-tan-neymar-va-mbappe.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Luis Garcia cho r\u1eb1ng Real Madrid n\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a PSG l\u00e0 Neymar v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe.</h2><h2>Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-neymar-gia-350-trieu-euro-180-188122.html\" target=\"_blank\">Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Real Madrid</span>. Ph\u00eda K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e0n ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng khi m\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo hay Karim Benzema b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u sa s\u00fat phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00ec tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Luis Garcia cho r\u1eb1ng b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Neymar \u2013 Mbappe s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o d\u00e0nh cho Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 TBN khuy\u00ean Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 TBN khuy\u00ean Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/real-duoc-khuyen-no-2-bom-tan-neymar-va-mbappe.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Garcia khuy\u00ean Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mbappe v\u00e0 Neymar</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cNeymar v\u00e0 Mbappe l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o d\u00e0nh cho Real Madrid. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u00ec Real s\u1ebd m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cReal Madrid lu\u00f4n nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Neymar \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 Mbappe c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 2 qu\u1ea3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d m\u00e0 Real c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u01b0ng b\u00e1 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n Real li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ed3n d\u1eadp sau khi Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00e0 Garcia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xoay quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang ta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghe r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tin \u0111\u1ed3n m\u1ed7i n\u0103m. \u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0 t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, Ronaldo t\u1eebng n\u00f3i nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. V\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u n\u00f3i \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u00e0 s\u0103m soi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ra sao. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid-172-190411.html\">Chelsea vu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t con m\u1ed3i v\u00ec... Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"912","checkdouble":"190413"},{"date":"11:39 05/07","title":"FIFA ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho Maradona v\u00ec th\u00f3i l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/5/fifa-dan-mat-maradona-vi-thoi-long-ngon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m x\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n trong m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, v\u1edbi m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u kh\u00f4ng n\u1ec3 nang ai sau tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Diego Maradona \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd n\u00e0y, FIFA c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u201cC\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng\u201d ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng gi\u00fap \u00edch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec th\u00ec th\u00f4i, \u0111\u1eb1ng n\u00e0y c\u00f2n t\u1ef1 b\u00eau x\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p trong m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh vi qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 Argentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u00f4 l\u1ed7 gi\u01a1 ng\u00f3n tay th\u1ed1i v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3, Maradona l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00e1n ng\u1ea9m b\u1edfi th\u00f3i l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-anh-tren-cham-11m-421-190321.html\" target=\"_blank\">Colombia vs Anh v\u00f2ng 1/8</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"FIFA c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o Maradona ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"FIFA c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o Maradona ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Maradona ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Colombia vs Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Maradona kh\u00f4ng \u01b0a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u00f4ng ghi \u1edf World Cup 1986, l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n x\u01b0a nay ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng m\u1eb7c \u00e1o Colombia \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Nam M\u1ef9. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 58 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ecf ra cay c\u00fa v\u00e0 l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u00ednh FIFA \u0111\u00e3 \u201c\u0103n c\u1eafp\u201d chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cKh\u00f3c thu\u00ea\u201d cho Colombia \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Maradona m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh L\u0110B\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi d\u1eb1n m\u1eb7t c\u1ea3. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3n t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 c\u1ee7a FIFA g\u1eedi \u201cC\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng\u201d khi \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00ec \u00f4ng:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cFIFA lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trong kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng l\u1eabn nhau \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, FIFA r\u1ea5t l\u1ea5y l\u00e0m ti\u1ebfc khi \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 h\u00e0m h\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i vi\u1ebft n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta.\u201d</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/maradona-xuat-vien-toi-dang-cang-tran-suc-song-hon-bao-gio-het-421-189895.html\">Maradona xu\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7n: \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u0103ng tr\u00e0n s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/vua-bong-da-maradona-treo-thuong-8000-bang-truy-tim-ke-tung-tin-minh-chet-188-190165.html\">Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Maradona treo th\u01b0\u1edfng 8.000 b\u1ea3ng truy t\u00ecm k\u1ebb tung tin m\u00ecnh ch\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"911","checkdouble":"190415"},{"date":"07:06 05/07","title":"Inter Milan \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/inter-milan-dang-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 5/7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/Lich_thi_dau_World_Cup_2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"> L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK World Cup 2018 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\nC\u1eadp nh\u1eadt nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK World Cup 2018 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 14.6 \u0111\u1ebfn 15.7.2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecon