 \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/kompany-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-bi-vs-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Brazil. Trung v\u1ec7 k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u n\u00e0y kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Neymar c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Brazil.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 v\u00ec Brazil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong khi Brazil v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Mexico 2-0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a Nacer Chadli \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 3-2. Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3, HLV Roberto Martinez tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Brazil t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Brazil c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u201cC\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng Brazil l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t trong World Cup 2018\u201d, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi khen nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd. Kh\u00f4ng ai trong \u0110T B\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t ng\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd thua Brazil.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Vincent Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Vincent-Kompany-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-Bi-vs-Brazil-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ec9 nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 3-2</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 nh\u1eefng pha 1 vs 1. H\u1ecd lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf ra m\u1ecdi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho nhau, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng theo quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kompany cua Bi\" title=\"Kompany cua Bi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/kompany-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-bi-vs-brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kompany ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Brazil \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o HLV Martinez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Roberto Martinez, B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. C\u1ef1u HLV Everton \u01b0a th\u00edch s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-4-3 \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. V\u00e0 Kompany kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng d\u00f9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ed7i trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi tri\u1ec3n m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d, Kompany n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p kh\u00e1c khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Brazil.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T B\u1ec9 tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-bi-32-nhat-ban-421-190297.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hazard-tiet-lo-su-khac-biet-cua-dt-bi-421-190265.html\">Hazard ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\">\u0110\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Samurai xanh c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9: S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lukaku</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-bi-32-nhat-ban-quy-do-no-samurai-loi-cam-on-421-190243.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf n\u1ee3 Samurai l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-man-nguoc-dong-kho-tin-cua-bi-truoc-nhat-ban-421-190239.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"909","checkdouble":"190392"},{"date":"07:34 05/07","title":"Mourinho b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e0i\u2026 \u201c\u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch\u201d c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-dt-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh \u0111ang d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u x\u1ea5u x\u00ed t\u1ea1i Moscow</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 do c\u00f4ng Harry Kane t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n nh\u01b0ng Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 3, trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho Colombia \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u00e1 th\u00eam kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T anh t\u1ecf ra chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c h\u01a1n trong c\u00e1c c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh \u0111ang d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh \u0111ang d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-dt-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n c\u00e3i v\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh x\u1ea5u x\u00ed. Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i, c\u00e3i v\u00e3 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft v\u1ee5n m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i. T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 8 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh r\u00fat ra v\u1edbi 6 cho Colombia, 2 cho Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh khi\u1ebfn cho HLV Jose Mourinho c\u1ee7a Man United ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00edch danh Harry Maguire, t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Leicester City c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0103n v\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho noi ve DT Duc sau tran thua soc\" title=\"Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/MU-muon-mua-Leonardo-Bonucci-voi-gia-37-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eadt. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch th\u00e1i qu\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d, Mourinho n\u00f3i tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a Nga. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi th\u1ea5y bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c trung v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 Harry Maguire.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t trung th\u1ef1c, nh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i ng\u00e3 v\u1edd trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i d\u00f9ng VAR. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0103n v\u1ea1, nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ng\u00e3 v\u1edd v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea5t \u0111i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Anh vs Colombia tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-chien-thang-cua-anh-truoc-colombia-421-190371.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/tai-sao-vardy-khong-duoc-da-luan-luu-truoc-colombia-469-190368.html\">T\u1ea1i sao Vardy kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/falcao-cay-cu-anh-chien-thang-vi-trong-tai-421-190363.html\">Falcao cay c\u00fa: Anh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00ec tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lingard-anh-da-cho-doi-ngay-nay-rat-lau-roi-421-190364.html\">Lingard: Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-colombia-tu-hao-du-bai-tran-truoc-anh-421-190358.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o d\u00f9 b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"908","checkdouble":"190394"},{"date":"07:21 05/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 05/07: MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d c\u00f9ng l\u00fac","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-0507-mu-va-chelsea-no-bom-tan-cung-luc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 05/07.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo; c\u00f9ng l\u00fac</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 0507 MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 0507 MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/chelsea-chi-ban-willian-cho-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Willian c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Sport Mediaset, MU v\u00e0 Chelsea nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i th\u00e1ng 7. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Chelsea chi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Gonzalo Higuain th\u00ec M.U b\u1ecf ra 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Wenger b\u1ecb ch\u00e2m bi\u1ebfm sau ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jordan Pickford, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Everton l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia. C\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh c\u00f9ng Stoke City. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y thay cho l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh nh\u01b0 Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league-172-190387.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league-172-190387.html\">Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool</span><br>\r\nXherdan Shaqiri mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League thay v\u00ec xu\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh c\u00f9ng Stoke City. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y thay cho l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang theo \u0111u\u1ed5i anh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Anh c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Vardy</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jamie Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0110T Anh cung c\u1ea5p.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t HLV b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i sau World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Oscar Ramirez bi Costa Rica sa thai\" title=\"Oscar Ramirez b\u1ecb Costa Rica sa th\u1ea3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/them-mot-hlv-bi-sa-thai-sau-world-cup-2018.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Oscar Ramirez b\u1ecb Costa Rica sa th\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Costa Rica sa th\u1ea3i HLV Oscar Ramirez \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Costa Rica, \u00f4ng Fedefutbol Rodolfo Villalobos x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/them-mot-hlv-bi-sa-thai-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190383.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/them-mot-hlv-bi-sa-thai-sau-world-cup-2018.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/them-mot-hlv-bi-sa-thai-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190383.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t HLV b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i sau World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nCosta Rica sa th\u1ea3i HLV Oscar Ramirez \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Costa Rica, \u00f4ng Fedefutbol Rodolfo Villalobos x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u00dd khuy\u00ean Neymar ng\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha &ldquo;\u0103n v\u1ea1&rdquo; t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 \u0110T \u00dd, Claudio Gentile \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i d\u1eebng vi\u1ec7c di\u1ec5n k\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea h\u1ecfi mua Mateo Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Everton chi 24 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mina ghi ban cho Colombia\" title=\"Mina ghi ban cho Colombia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-47-MU-quan-tam-sao-tuyen-Croatia-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton mu\u1ed1n mua Mina&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Liverpool Echo, Everton s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 24 tri\u1ec7u euro mua trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eeba c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kante \u01b0u ti\u00ean PSG h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Mirror, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p r\u1eddi Chelsea ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kante \u01b0u ti\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 cho PSG thay v\u00ec kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"907","checkdouble":"190395"},{"date":"08:23 05/07","title":"C\u1ef1u HLV Anh b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/cuu-hlv-anh-bat-ngo-ung-ho-thuy-dien-chien-thang.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ef1c ra th\u00ec c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f4i khi Sven-Goran Eriksson v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1eafc \u00c2u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y kia.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 v\u00e0 Colombia theo nh\u1eefng k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh h\u1eb9n g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Tam S\u01b0 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 28 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Erikson n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Erikson n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/cuu-hlv-anh-bat-ngo-ung-ho-thuy-dien-chien-thang.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Erikson n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Andreas Granqvist kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/granqvist-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-thuy-dien-vs-anh-421-190391.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh</span>, HLV Sven-Goran Eriksson c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tam S\u01b0 nh\u1eefng n\u0103m \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1eadp ni\u00ean 2000:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i tin m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd d\u00e0nh cho Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Anh c\u00f2n ghi n\u1ed5i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra khi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 lo\u1ea1i \u00dd tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn Nga v\u1edbi m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch, trong khi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0 Harry Kane, nh\u01b0ng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mang s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 Eriksson n\u00f3i, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu cho Anh khi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng thua trong hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp (2002 v\u00e0 2006, khi ch\u00ednh Eriksson d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Tam S\u01b0). \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Croatia ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-ay-la-zlatan-nhung-chung-ta-la-thuy-dien-421-188871.html\">Anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 Zlatan, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-nguoi-hung-emil-forsberg-421-190326.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n-kh\u00f4ng-Ibra ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf World Cup: H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh phi th\u01b0\u1eddng vi\u1ebft b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"906","checkdouble":"190396"}]}